PROCEDURE Modify-Selection :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:    Change the value of the currently selected file.
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/*  DEFINE VAR l_ok     AS LOGICAL   NO-UNDO.*/
/*  DEFINE VAR new_file AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.*/
